<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4896978>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 4. Psilotreta flavida sp. nov. 4A, male head, dorsal; 4B, same, left lateral; 4C, male right wings, dorsal; 4D–4I, male genitalia: 4D, left lateral; 4E, left lateral process & intermediate appendage of segment X, left lateral; 4F, phallus, left lateral; 4G, phallus, ventral; 4H, dorsal; 4I, ventral. 4I–4J, female genitalia: 4J, dorsal; 4K, ventral.Abbreviations: aed. = aedeagus; avs. = anterior vaginal sclerite; end. = endotheca; int.app. = intermediate appendage (paired); lat.pr. = lateral process (paired); par. = paramere (paired); phall. = phallotheca; pvs. = posterior vaginal sclerite; sIX = sternum IX; v.pr. = ventral projection (paired)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4896978/files/figure.png" .

